# Canonical author identity for the AttnFuse repository.
#
# The mailmap re-attributes commits with the email on the right to the
# identity on the left. GitHub respects this file when computing the
# contributor list, so any commit whose author or co-author field
# happens to contain a generic / non-canonical email will still be
# displayed as the canonical author below.
#
# Format:  Canonical Name <canonical@email>   <alias@email>
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap

Varun Kumar Dasoju <the.v007@icloud.com>  <noreply@anthropic.com>
